<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> tiripuvaṉac cakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> vicaiyakaṇṭakopāla tevarkku yāṇṭu <num value="19"><g type="numeral">10</g> 9</num>vatu ceyaṅkoṇṭa coḻamaṇṭalattut tāmaṟ
<lb n="2"/>koṭṭattu tiruppuṭkuḻi nāyaṉārkku tiruviḷakkukku Āntai nāṭṭil Irukkum Uṭaiyāṉ koṉmakaṉ periyaperumāḷāṉa Amarakoṉ
<lb n="3"/>tai mātam viṭṭa pacu 8 Ippacu Eṭṭum kaikkoṇṭu kālviḷakku cantirātittavarai naṭattakaṭavom tiruppuṭkuḻi nāyaṉār koyil
<lb n="4"/>tāṉattā rom<hi rend="grantha">ḥ §</hi>
</p>

